{"tid":2346095,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"犯法要負責 ︱聲稱遭親友孤立警員 偷信用卡狂碌買iPhone 判囚5個月","createTime":"2020-12-30T04:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T06:25:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":24,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"f689e72339ac1efe40f2f9592f7cd3646b3a537f","tid":2346095,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:32:37.000Z","msg":"機動部隊警員聲稱因社會運動而遭親友孤立，情緒打擊下終日自閉在家。及後他於休班時在戲院取去別人遺下的信用卡，繼而瘋狂碌卡購物，包括在Apple Store購買兩部手機，涉款約2.5萬元。警員早前承認盜竊罪及以欺騙手段取得財產罪，求情強調在警隊中從未做過錯事。裁判官張志偉今判處涉案警員入獄5個月。<br />\n<br />\n現已被停職的被告李卓軒（28歲）早前求情指，自2011年中七畢業後，曾任職不同工作，三年前加入警隊，短時間內減去60磅，通過體能測試完成課程。惟自去年社會運動後，被告因警員身份而遭親友疏遠，感到鬱悶，終日自閉在家，友人更向他借貸五萬元不還。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/M5UZIJQ2PFAJDO7RW5B4MRFQJ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FM5UZIJQ2PFAJDO7RW5B4MRFQJ4%2F&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSNnRRycoFBIefads3zMUO1U%3D&h=37e45d11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201230%2FM5UZIJQ2PFAJDO7RW5B4MRFQJ4%2F&h=c0cd782e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201230/M5UZIJQ2PFAJDO7RW5B4MRFQJ4/</a>"},{"pid":"2cecab324246011a4bbe02b4adc42202862edb74","tid":2346095,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:33:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442bdc78ae3c64f8ce5bc5a5ade4ddc4145de1e9","tid":2346095,"uid":57303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T04:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6585bd80ac6e696b7e53b1e8e983abc5817c5e3","tid":2346095,"uid":2403